        <Parent_String>calf (leather) [300227525], leather by origin [300263009], leather [300011845], processed animal material [300193287], animal material [300011793], biological material [300265629], materials by origin [300206573], materials (substances) [300010358], Materials (hierarchy name) [300010357], Materials Facet [300264091]</Parent_String>
